name: Dimensional Delivery
description:
DIMENSIONAL DELIVERY

As an interdimensional deliveryman who can phase between worlds at will, your services are always in demand. Hop from one to the other to complete your route safely and make sure everyone on both sides of reality gets their deliveries. For an extra challenge, lookout for lost packages along the way. It's easy for things to get lost in the shuffle when it's the whole world getting shuffled, after all.

KEYBOARD CONTROLS:

Move: A/D or Left/Right Arrow

Jump: Space Bar

Phase: Left or Right Shift

Reset: Delete

XBOX CONTROLLER CONTROLS:

Move: Left Analog Stick

Jump: A

Phase: B

Reset: Select
